query:
SELECT 
  p.countryId,
  p.serviceId,
  p.apiId,
  COUNT(*) as count,
  GROUP_CONCAT(p.id) as ids
FROM prices p
GROUP BY p.countryId, p.serviceId, p.apiId
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
ORDER BY count DESC;
